channel.title: Gain a level then logs out?
channel.description:
Ok I have my server and everytimg you get a level you get logged out (NOTE: this is Project Delta Force). So if I type master, I get all 99's and I get logged out, log back in and I have all 99 stats and 126 combat level. I added a dummy and when you click on it you gain 11 levels, then you get logged out. How can I fix this (I have a video I will add it when youtube accepts it)?
[url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=YMpXoik9NDA]http://youtube.com/watch?v=YMpXoik9NDA[/url]
EDIT: ADDED VID!
